data.description: Beautiful Ranch, brick home with 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath, attached carport and metal roof on 1 acre lot including a Storage building on 1.5 acre lot. Home offers original hardwood floors throughout, large livingroom with lots of natural light. Kitchen with plenty of counter space and granite counters, all wood cabinets (will need appliances). Bedrooms are a great size, screened front porch to enjoy the sunrise and sunset. This property offers a detached 2 car garage and large metal carport and tons of storage options. Plenty space for chicken coop and horse friendly.
